name: Most High
description:
Chorus
Throw your hands in the sky, If you feel like I feel, Get them up, Wave them High,
Throw your hands in the sky, If you feel like I feel, Get them up, Wave them High,
To the most high, To the most high up, To the most high, To the most high up,
Verse
I thank God for the first amendment, Freedom of speech, So I can say this,
Freedom of religion, so it don’t really matter if I claim I’m a Christian,
Let me help you see my vision, We can all have peace here under the sun,
We can exhale hate and inhale love, That’s if we all had trust in the one above,
Chorus
Throw your hands in the sky, If you feel like I feel, Get them up, Wave them High,
Throw your hands in the sky, If you feel like I feel, Get them up, Wave them High,
To the most high, to the most high up, To the most high, to the most high up,
Verse
People might think I’m crazy because I talk about religion, my vision and my beliefs,
Which started after AD, Yea I’m talking about J.C.,
Get in touch with your history, It’s all still a mystery depending on what you read,
Or you could believe what you see, Which could be nothing or everything.
